// symref - AI Context Window Solution
// Version: 2025.02

// Context Limitations & Solutions
1. Limited Visibility:
   symref refs yourFunction -d ./src         // Full codebase view
   symref refs "main,*" --include "src/*.ts" // Entry points
   symref refs "*Service*" -d ./src          // Dependency chain

2. Implementation Gaps:
   symref refs IYourInterface -d ./src     // Interface impl
   symref refs modifiedFunction -d ./src   // Update tracking
   symref dead src/file.ts                 // Dead code

// Quick Commands
1. Find Refs:
   symref refs MyClass
   symref refs myFunc,IMyInterface

2. Dead Check:
   symref dead src/components/MyComp.ts

// Options
-d <path>      // Base dir
-p <path>      // tsconfig
--include      // Include files
--exclude      // Exclude files

// Features
1. Symbol Analysis:
   - Finds refs & definitions
   - Shows context & usage

2. Dead Code:
   - Finds unused code
   - Reports refs

// Output
✓ Found refs:  file.ts:line (context)
⚠ No refs:     Consider removal

// Best Practice
1. Pre-change: Check refs & usage
2. Cleanup:    Remove unused, update docs

// Core
@[staticCodeChecker.ts] - Analyzer
@[cli.ts] - CLI
@[README.md] - Docs